data.description: REDUCED PRICE! PROJECTED RENTAL INCOME OF $57k+! Unique Island home offering rear decking with POOL, Tiki Bar, dining space & sitting area. Main living space is on the second level. Adorable vinyl front porch, open concept living room, dining area & kitchen w vaulted ceiling, ship lap accent walls, gas fireplace, large island w built in microwave, cabinets, quartz countertops & wine fridge! Amazing space & light. Two bedrooms plus a primary suite! Suite offers 3 closets, one is walk in, full bath w French doors, two vanities, garden spa tub, shower & bidet. Additional full bath & half bath. Ground level w heated office, family room, pool table & storage. OVERSIZED detached garage, paved driveway, fenced front yard. New home to be build on adj parcel. 2021 renovation/roof. Sq Ft both levels
